for t in range(int(input())):
 n=int(input())
 a=list(map(int,input().split()))
 s=0
 l=[]
 for i in range(n):
  if (a[i]<0):
   e=i
   ss=sum(a[s:e])
   l.append((ss,e-s,n-s))
   s=i+1
 e=n
 ss=sum(a[s:e])
 l.append((ss,e-s,n-s))
 x=max(l)
 s=n-x[2]
 e=x[1]+s
 for i in range(s,e):
  print(a[i], end=' ')
 print("")
